Ngibona sekufike lapho sekufanele silinde, sikhuzane ngoba lolu daba luvele lusezithebeni zenkantolo emva kokuba kukhuthazwe uBabes Wodumo ngokwesekwa okukhulu ukuba asivulele icala isithandwa sakhe, asiqophe simbeka isandla simusho ngamagama alumelayo. Okuqaphelekayo wukuthi akekho engisamuzwa ethuswa ngamagama aqosheme aphimiswa nguBabes Wodumo kodwa singeke sakukhuthaza ukuziphindiselela kukaMampitsha ngokumbeka isandla. Umbuzo ovukayo ngesihloko sikamfowethu ozibize ngoThabo Sikhosana uthi kungenzeke yini ukuthi naye uBabes usenza izidomu ngoba akavezi ukuthi ingxabano iqale kanjani nokuthi umasihlalisane wakhe uze amsole ngokususa uthuthuva etheleka entathakusa nje wayevela kuphi? Mangikucacise ukuthi angikaze ngibe wumlandeli wabo bobabili ngenxa yokungayithandi indlela abaqopha ngayo ama-video abo nemidanso yakhona. Ngingasayiphathi-ke eyokugqoka. Bengifisa sizifundise ukulinda uma udaba olunjengalolu selusezithebeni zenkantolo. Kuyaxaka nokho okosopolitiki ngoba angikhumbuli bekhuthaza noma beseka odadewethu abaqhamuka nezinsolo zokuhlukumezeka ezibhekiswe kozakwabo njengoba beseka uBabes Wodumo. Angisayiphathi ekayise, ozwakale efudumala emsakazweni, ethi ingane yakhe ngendlela ephazamiseke ngayo iyothola ukwelashwa kanti izovela isedilini leziphuzo, zona lezi zohlobo ebezisolwa nguMampintsha. Ngiyafisa mhla lufika esiphethweni udaba kube khona intatheli noma umsakazi ozomqonda ngqo umgcotshwa onguyise kaBabes asikhanyisele phakathi kukaBongekile amkhulise ekhaya noBabes wodumo wezobumnandi. Okunye okuqaphelekayo wukungaphawuli komndeni kaMandla Maphumulo. Sengiphetha, akungathi ekugcineni sekukhulunywe kangaka sithole ukuthi oxamu babhaxulana ngemisila kulolu daba.  Nkosinathi Qwabe EMGUNGUNDLOVU